data.name: achievementHelp
data.value:
Achievements are intented to show off about what players have achieved by using it and playing I.G.I.-2. It helps to grow the reputation among public, and proves how much the player is dedicated & stronger to play.
There are three types of achievements featured in Centaurus, viz. Join Records, ChatUp Records, Login Records.
• The Join Records achievement is dependent upon how many times you joins the game to play. Once you reach the Bronze badge (3rd from the last legend ones), you may thereafter change your name with no restrictions!
• The ChatUp Records is achieved when you start chatting in ChatUp of Centaurus.
• The Login Records is based on how many times you use the CentoProtector (protection service of Centaurus) to sign in.
• The Game Time Records is a new type of achievement introduced in 3.0. It is dependent upon how much time you have played the game in lifetime.
Bonus Point: You earn +3 bonus point for all achievements when you have unlocked an achievement of any type. It is all about to make I.G.I.-2 great again!

data.name: chatRules
data.value:
Before starting and chatting among buddies, you must have some intuition about communicating rules & regulations listed below:
1. The time is synchronized with GMT+5:30 (Indian Standard Time), so, the time might be different for your country if you belongs to somewhere else.
2. This is a public chat, so chat smart & do not use any abusive language or any hate speech.
3. Do not spam in chat to disturb anyone if you have nothing relevant to do with corresponding discussion(s).
4. You are allowed to send 64 letters every message in order to keep the chatting clean.
5. Each message must contain at least 3 letters.
6. Respect everyone and keep the discussions clean.
7. The privacy is in your hand. Do not share your credentials, sensitive information such as public IP address, etc. ChatUp service shall not be liable for any casualties due to sharing them.

data.name: didYouKnow
data.value: Centaurus was born on 26th January 2020 Clicking on the warmcome header will change it into different color effects You can do hangouts with other buddies in ChatUp to call them in game You can use Wait for Somebody to Join when nobody's in game You can view your achievements & progression in My Track You don't need to check for Centaurus updates or any other systematic stuffs because they are completely automated You can download your favorable or server required maps from MapDown instantly You can boost performance of Centaurus from Edit Features option You can manually join any server from Manual Server Joiner Now you can control Centaurus appearance on your device startup from Miscellaneous menu You should always keep your Centaurus protected with CentoProtector You can take backup of your scores before formatting your PC from My Track Progression's settings You can restart Centaurus by pressing Ctrl+Shift+Z if you are facing any problem If you did already export your Centaurus scores then you can import it back too Centaurus begin counting how long have you played whenever you start playing I.G.I.-2 Community: You can join our Facebook community or visit our website Community: You can read our F.A.Q. questions directly in-app Community: You can suggest new features and/or report cheaters or violators Community: You can contact one of the admins from Contact to Admin system A top secret feature for a few chosen players also exists

data.name: security
data.value:
You are optionally but highly recommended to set a password for Centaurus to make it secure from others in your device except those who already knows your set password (if any).
It is because other people in your computer may access it too and play, somehow if they does something bad, only you shall be responsible for any fatality. Therefore you are recommended to protect your launcher.

data.name: syncError
data.value:
We are unable to synchronize your Centaurus to the server. YOU CAN CONTINUE USING OTHER FEATURES EXCEPT PLAYING THE MULTIPLAYER AFTER CLOSING THIS PAGE.
The possible cause of this issue is listed along the possibility:
1. Your internet connectivity may be disturbed. (most possible) 2. Your IP range is yet blocked. (more possible) 3. The server is really down. (less possible) 4. Your Centaurus is not given access to the internet from the firewall. (least possible)
Note: If you are getting this problem again and again and not finding it solved from 'Click to know what can you do...' suggestions, then you may need to fill up a complain form which could be found by clicking the button placed below.

data.name: syncSolution
data.value:
Here is what could you do before applying a complaint form:
> Try restarting your network connection by switching it off and on. > Check if your network is correctly connected to a network. > Go to RUN (Win+R), type 'cleanmgr' and clean up the junk files. > The final solution: Change the I.G.I.-2 folder 'pc' into 'pc1' or something else and allow the Centaurus from your firewall.
Fill up the form and submit if none of the above did work successfully. You can contact an active admin for help and receive replies from them.

data.name: waitRecommendation
data.value:
Are you sure you want to turn on Waiting Mode? It is because probably somebody else might have already turned on waiting mode for another player to join. It is highly recommended to join and wait for at least 10 minutes before using this feature.
Click 'Yes' to ignore and start waiting, 'No' to join game and see if somebody comes (recommended primarily), 'Cancel' to do nothing & quit from this box.
